          <div class="col-lg-6 pt-4 pt-lg-0 order-2 order-lg-1 content">
                <h3>Empowering Minds, Elevating Futures: Discover Excellence with EduSmart.</h3>
            <p class="fst-italic">
                    At EduSmart, we are passionate about empowering students to unlock their full potential and achieve academic excellence. With 3 years of experience, we have established ourselves as a trusted provIder of comprehensive and personalized educational support. Our team of more than a hundred highly qualified and collaborative tutors is devoted to helping students succeed.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our core values:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i>
                        Collaboration: We foster a collaborative partnership between our tutors, students, and parents to ensure everyone is working together towards shared goals. We believe in open communication, active listening, and creating a positive and inclusive learning community.

                    </li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i>
                        Personalization: We recognize that every student is unique, with individual strengths, challenges, and learning styles. Our personalized approach ensures that we tailor our instruction and support to meet the specific needs of each student.
                    </li>
              <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i>
                        Flexibility: We understand that students have diverse schedules and commitments. We offer flexible learning options to accommodate their needs, whether it's through in-person sessions, online tutoring, or a blend of both. We believe in adapting our services to provide convenient and accessible learning experiences.
                    </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                    At EduSmart, we believe that education is not just about grades, but also about cultivating a passion for learning, critical thinking, and personal growth. Our dedicated team is committed to building strong relationships with our students, provIding mentorship that goes beyond academics. We are here to inspire, motivate, and empower you to achieve your full potential!
                </p>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
